      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><style>[data-colorid=qb39hh2648]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qb39hh2648]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=srwm7iaczi]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=srwm7iaczi]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=eackq1kbf8]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=eackq1kbf8]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=d1w6qwaz6l]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=d1w6qwaz6l]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=sh4a5bchbd]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=sh4a5bchbd]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=etap9k31xg]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=etap9k31xg]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=cscxezqulb]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cscxezqulb]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=e6k7173cex]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=e6k7173cex]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=v5fdzfc2wc]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=v5fdzfc2wc]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=oxzmqbl2go]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=oxzmqbl2go]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=g5uyqpyh7g]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=g5uyqpyh7g]{color:#4c9fc2}</style><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"ultraman-docs.webp\" width=\"1678\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542221690/ultraman-docs.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762914034911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1678&amp;height=707\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542221690/ultraman-docs.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762914034911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1079\" data-width=\"2560\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663420990\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ultraman-docs.webp\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/webp\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542221690\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"16df92b0-8869-4621-a9b0-7ebbeb67961e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542221690/ultraman-docs.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762914034911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=1079 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542221690/ultraman-docs.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762914034911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1678&amp;height=707 1x\" /></span><p local-id=\"f52e5f4c6f0f\" /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-local-id=\"21d8df1a290d\" data-macro-id=\"95671167-43bb-4bfa-8f75-96ee51e5b925\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 local-id=\"0bf4e9d0040d\" id=\"StylizedLooks-Licensing\">Licensing</h3><p local-id=\"be1dd0bf2059\"><strong> Stylized Looks</strong> is only available to commercial customers of RenderMan.</p></div></div><p local-id=\"0fe33f730293\" /><p local-id=\"f95d63bf49cb\"><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">The innovative Stylized Looks toolset allows RenderMan to deliver images beyond photorealism. Artists can render images that look like cartoons, illustrations, or watercolors. This flexible system allows the creation of unique looks and is limited only by imagination.</span></p><hr local-id=\"f6a7a471b4ec\" /><h1 local-id=\"8564909d56a6\" id=\"StylizedLooks-What’snewinRenderMan27StylizedLooks\">What&rsquo;s new in RenderMan 27 Stylized Looks</h1><h4 local-id=\"e5f0b4a7b57b\" id=\"StylizedLooks-NewFiltersinXPU\">New Filters in XPU</h4><p local-id=\"10dffca09d0b\">PxrStylized<strong>LinesXPU</strong><br />PxrStylized<strong>CanvasXPU</strong><br />PxrStylized<strong>HatchingSampleXPU</strong><br />PxrStylized<strong>PainterlyBrushXPU</strong><br />PxrStylized<strong>ToonXPU</strong></p><h4 local-id=\"2d11aa64a1cd\" id=\"StylizedLooks-NewShadersinXPU&amp;RIS\">New Shaders in XPU &amp; RIS</h4><p local-id=\"8ce8fb8f6c38\">PxrStylized<strong>PainterlyBrushControl</strong><br />PxrStylized<strong>LightControl </strong>(RM 27.2)<br />PxrStylized<strong>LinesControl </strong>(RM 27.2)<br />PxrStylized<strong>HatchControl </strong>(RM 27.2)</p><h4 local-id=\"82a6cda7ab33\" id=\"StylizedLooks-UpdatedShadersinXPU&amp;RIS\">Updated Shaders in XPU &amp; RIS</h4><p local-id=\"f409f9a36497\">PxrStylized<strong>Control</strong></p><h1 local-id=\"3392e5335ae8\" id=\"StylizedLooks-HighlightsofStylizedLooks:\"><span data-colorid=\"e6k7173cex\">Highlights of Stylized Looks :</span><br /></h1><h4 local-id=\"439caf0b9893\" id=\"StylizedLooks-RenderinRenderMan..PostProcessedwithStylizedLooks\"><span data-colorid=\"eackq1kbf8\">Render in RenderMan .. Post Processed with Stylized Looks</span></h4><p local-id=\"510b6a03f224\"><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Stylized Looks are a pixel-by-pixel post-process that is applied after your image is rendered (or during an IPR session), handled by 3 various Display Filters (PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching)</span><br /><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Create your scenes using all the tools within the powerful RenderMan toolkit, including PxrSurface, Lama, and RenderMan lights .. then transform to Stylized Looks!</span></p><p local-id=\"dd717d5cdf7e\" /><h4 local-id=\"555547ea9639\" id=\"StylizedLooks-MixPhotorealistic&amp;Stylized...allinonerender!\"><span data-colorid=\"oxzmqbl2go\">Mix Photorealistic &amp; Stylized ... all in one render!</span></h4><p local-id=\"df5954809604\">Create incredible imagery using RenderMan Lights to control the transition between photoreal and stylized.&nbsp;<br />For instance, use the beam from a&nbsp;PxrRectLight&nbsp;to add hatching to a photoreal render.&nbsp; Wherever the light strikes ... hatching is applied</p><p local-id=\"91ae81f284d8\" /><h4 local-id=\"45441d732dd5\" id=\"StylizedLooks-Createyourowntexturessets\"><span data-colorid=\"g5uyqpyh7g\">Create your own textures sets</span></h4><p local-id=\"b854e5770db1\">Stylized Looks not only ships with a number of texture presets, but you also can create and use your own unique texture sets.<br />Need a specific NPR to look at?&nbsp; No problem ... create your own hatching texture sets!<br /></p><h4 local-id=\"09a7ca3ae77e\" id=\"StylizedLooks-Toon+Illustrative/HatchingLighting+Lines\"><span data-colorid=\"etap9k31xg\">Toon + Illustrative/Hatching Lighting + Lines</span></h4><p local-id=\"2a4c9613aea5\"><strong>Toon</strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">: Quantize any signal per light (diffuse, spec, refraction, &hellip;) with controllable steps</span><br /><strong>Illustrative Hatching Lighting:</strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> Dynamically based on light or camera depth for illustrative light &amp; shadow rendering</span><br /><strong>Lines</strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">: Linework with line thickness, line thickness by lighting, line thickness by custom per object, line color by albedo, line color by lighting, line color by custom per object settings</span><br /></p><h4 local-id=\"d7bc82cdb5db\" id=\"StylizedLooks-Mix&amp;MatchStyles\"><span data-colorid=\"v5fdzfc2wc\">Mix &amp; Match Styles</span></h4><p local-id=\"1cf20019fd93\"><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Mix and match unique and creative combinations of&nbsp;PxrStylizedToon / PxrStylizedLines / PxrStylizedHatching display filters</span><br />Try layering multiple PxrStylizedLines, each with a different thickness to create beautiful and artistic interior and exterior linework.</p><p local-id=\"8c25609be58d\" /><h4 local-id=\"18352cef1a34\" id=\"StylizedLooks-Globalandper-objectcontrol\"><span data-colorid=\"cscxezqulb\">Global and per-object control</span><br /></h4><p local-id=\"05ead628599b\"><span data-colorid=\"sh4a5bchbd\">Attach the PxrStylizedControl to your PxrSurface &amp; LamaSurface nodes to control your entire scene or per object.</span><br /><span data-colorid=\"qb39hh2648\">Control different line thicknesses/coloring for certain objects</span></p><p local-id=\"de1399d7c790\" /><h4 local-id=\"8aa59ed85c4e\" id=\"StylizedLooks-ExportAOVsforextrarefinement\"><span data-colorid=\"d1w6qwaz6l\">Export AOVs for extra refinement</span></h4><p local-id=\"04bc5b3a3261\"><span data-colorid=\"srwm7iaczi\">All AOVs associated with Stylized Looks can be exported for further creative refinement and layering outside of RenderMan</span></p><p local-id=\"0565d78e3575\" /><p local-id=\"32304de62bc9\" /><hr local-id=\"7ba88b80e978\" /><p local-id=\"08e21f4c9d26\" /><p local-id=\"5d944bf34c7d\" /><ul class=\"childpages-macro conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"35b0028c-1d10-461f-978a-238a45df9854\" data-macro-id=\"551e3303-d35e-4dd0-92b9-7e3516898760\" data-macro-name=\"children\"><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221735/Getting+Started+with+Stylized+Looks\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221735\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Started with Stylized Looks</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542222104/Stylized+Looks+Gallery\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222104\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Looks Gallery</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221812/Stylized+Canvas\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221812\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Canvas</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221833/Stylized+Hatching\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221833\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Hatching</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221920/Stylized+Lines\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221920\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Lines</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221952/Stylized+Toon\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221952\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Toon</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542221999/Stylized+Control\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542221999\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Control</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542222017/Stylized+AOVs\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222017\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized AOVs</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/662372354/Stylized+Painterly+Brush+Control\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662372354\" data-linked-resource-version=\"20\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Painterly Brush Control</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/662667265/Stylized+Painterly+Brush+XPU\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662667265\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Painterly Brush XPU</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/662241282/Stylized+Lines+XPU\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662241282\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Lines XPU</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/662798337/Stylized+Hatching+Sample+XPU\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662798337\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Hatching Sample XPU</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/662798351/Stylized+Toon+XPU\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662798351\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Toon XPU</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/668336138/Stylized+Canvas+XPU\" data-linked-resource-id=\"668336138\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Canvas XPU</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/869007361/Stylized+Lines+Control\" data-linked-resource-id=\"869007361\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Lines Control</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/869007420/Stylized+Hatch+Control\" data-linked-resource-id=\"869007420\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Hatch Control</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/869007484/Stylized+Light+Control\" data-linked-resource-id=\"869007484\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Stylized Light Control</a></li></ul>"
    }
